          | &lt;div class="input-group flex-nowrap"&gt;
          |   &lt;span class="input-group-text" id="addon-wrapping"&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;
          |   &lt;input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Username" aria-label="Username" aria-describedby="addon-wrapping"&gt;
          | &lt;/div&gt;

      h4 Sizing
      p Add the relative form sizing classes to the <code>.input-group</code> itself and contents within will automatically resize—no need for repeating the form control size classes on each element.
      p
        strong Sizing on the individual input group elements isn’t supported.

      .bd-example
        .input-group.input-group-sm.mb-3
          span#inputGroup-sizing-sm.input-group-text Small
          input.form-control(type='text', aria-label='Sizing example input', aria-describedby='inputGroup-sizing-sm')
        .input-group.mb-3
          span#inputGroup-sizing-default.input-group-text Default
          input.form-control(type='text', aria-label='Sizing example input', aria-describedby='inputGroup-sizing-default')
        .input-group.input-group-lg
          span#inputGroup-sizing-lg.input-group-text Large
          input.form-control(type='text', aria-label='Sizing example input', aria-describedby='inputGroup-sizing-lg')

